Insider Activity


Individual




Thomas C. Ruffing



Mr. Thomas C. Ruffing is a Managing Director & Head-Asset Management at Blackstone Mortgage Trust, Inc., a Managing Director at BXMT Advisors LLC, and a Managing Director at Blackstone Real Estate Debt Strategies.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Virginia, a graduate degree from the University of Virginia, and an MBA from Columbia Business School.



