                                                    BRIEF-Blackstone Mortgage Trust qtrly EPS $0.53
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    4:50 PM ET 07/25/2017
                                                


Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc (BXMT): * Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT) reports second quarter 2017 results. * Qtrly gaap earnings per share $0.53. * Qtrly core earnings per share $0.60. * Qtrly book value of $26.38 per share, up $0.10 from prior quarter. * Q2 earnings per share view $0.62 -- Thomson Reuters I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust Reports Second Quarter 2017 Results
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:16 PM ET 07/25/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, July 25, 2017  Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT), Inc. today reported its second quarter 2017 results. Stephen D. Plavin, Chief Executive Officer, said, "We originated $1.5 billion of new loans in the quarter supported by $762 million of new capital markets transactions as we continue to deliver on our senior, floating rate strategy.

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust Announces Second Quarter 2017 Earnings Release and Conference Call
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    5:00 PM ET 07/06/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, July 6, 2017 Blackstone Mortgage Trust, Inc. (BXMT) today announced that it will publish its second quarter 2017 earnings presentation on its website at www.bxmt.com and file its Form 10-Q after market close on Tuesday, July 25, 2017. The company will also host a conference call to review results on Wednesday, July 26, 2017 at 10:00 am EDT.

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust declares $0.62 per share dividend
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:16 PM ET 06/13/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, June 13, 2017  Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT), Inc. today declared a dividend of $0.62 per share of class A common stock with respect to the second quarter of 2017. About Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT) Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT) is a real estate finance company that originates senior loans collateralized by commercial real estate in North America and Europe.

















                                                    Technical Insights on REIT Stocks -- Gaming and Leisure Properties, Lamar Advertising, Blackstone Mortgage Trust, and Douglas Emmett
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    6:55 AM ET 06/07/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, June 7, 2017 On Tuesday, benchmark US indices were in bearish colors as the NASDAQ Composite closed the trading session down 0.33%; the Dow Jones Industrial Average edged 0.23% lower; and the S&P 500 was down 0.28%. US markets made broad based losses with six out of nine sectors finishing the day in red. http://dailystocktracker.com/register/ Gaming and Leisure Properties . On Tuesday...

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust to Present at the JMP Securities 2017 Financial Services & Real Estate Conference
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    5:00 PM ET 06/02/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, June 2, 2017 Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT) announced today that Steve Plavin, President and Chief Executive Officer, will present at the JMP Securities 2017 Financial Services & Real Estate Conference in New York, New York on Thursday, June 22, 2017 at 11:00 am ET.

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust Announces Full Exercise Of Underwriters' Over-Allotment Option And Issuance Of Additional Convertible Senior Notes
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    5:00 PM ET 05/23/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, May 23, 2017  Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT), Inc. today announced that, in connection with the Company's underwritten public offering of its 4.375% convertible senior notes due 2022, the underwriters have exercised in full their option to purchase an additional $37.5 million aggregate principal amount of the Notes. The issuance of the additional Notes closed on May 23, 2017.

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust to Present at the KBW 2017 Mortgage Finance Conference
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    5:00 PM ET 05/15/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, May 15, 2017  Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT) announced today that Steve Plavin, President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in a fireside chat discussion at the Keefe, Bruyette & Woods 2017 Mortgage Finance Conference in New York, NY on Thursday, June 1, 2017 at 10:20 am ET.

















                                                    BRIEF-Blackstone Mortgage Trust prices public offering of convertible senior notes
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    8:37 PM ET 05/01/2017
                                                


Blackstone mortgage Trust (BXMT). * Blackstone mortgage Trust (BXMT) announces pricing of public offering of convertible senior notes. * Notes will pay interest semiannually at a rate of 4.375% per annum and will mature on may 5, 2022. * Pricing of underwritten public offering of $250 million aggregate principal amount of 4.375% convertible senior notes due 2022 Source text for Eikon:

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust Announces Pricing Of Public Offering Of Convertible Senior Notes
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    8:30 PM ET 05/01/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, May 1, 2017  Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT), Inc. today announced the pricing of an underwritten public offering of $250.0 million aggregate principal amount of its 4.375% convertible senior notes due 2022.

















                                                    BRIEF-Blackstone Mortgage Trust reports offering of convertible senior notes
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    7:20 AM ET 05/01/2017
                                                


Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc (BXMT): * Blackstone Mortgage Trust (BXMT), Inc. Announces public offering of convertible senior notes. * Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc (BXMT) - commenced underwritten public offering of $250.0 million aggregate principal amount of convertible senior notes due 2022.

















                                                    Blackstone Mortgage Trust, Inc. Announces Public Offering of Convertible Senior Notes
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    7:01 AM ET 05/01/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, May 1, 2017 Blackstone Mortgage Trust, Inc. (BXMT) today announced it has commenced an underwritten public offering of $250.0 million aggregate principal amount of convertible senior notes due 2022.












